category_redirect-change-category:
Used as comment. Parameters:
* %(oldCatLink)s - old category name
* %(oldCatTitle)s - old category name
* %(newCatLink)s - new category name
* %(newCatTitle)s - new category name
category_redirect-comment: Edit summary for maintenance notice of new redirects created.
category_redirect-edit-request:
Variables:
* %(itemlists)s - list of edit requests (pages). Uses the message {{msg-pywikibot|Category redirect-edit-request-item}}.
category_redirect-edit-request-item: Used as %(itemlist)s in {{msg-pywikibot|Category_redirect-edit-request}}. Variables: * %(title)s - page title * %(oldcat)s - old category name * %(newcat)s - new category name
category_redirect-fix-double: Edit summary when the bot fixes double category redirects.
category_redirect-log-added: Log message indicating category redirect template was added to the category page.
category_redirect-log-add-failed: Log message indicating category redirect template could not be added to the category page.
category_redirect-log-double: Log message indicating category redirect chain was fixed.
category_redirect-log-failed: Log message indicating category redirect chain could not be solved.
category_redirect-log-false-positive: Log message indicating category page was not redirect.
category_redirect-log-ignoring: Log message indicating category page is a redirect on purpose.
category_redirect-log-loop: Log message indicating category redirect chain makes a loop.
category_redirect-log-moved: Log message indicating pages found and moved from the redirected category.
category_redirect-log-move-error: Log message indicating category contents could not be moved.
category_redirect-log-not-loaded: Log message indicating category page could not be loaded.
category_redirect-log-skipping: Log message indicating bot is not ready to edit the page.
category_redirect-older-logs: Link to older logs from the log page
category_redirect-problem-hard: Log message indicating category redirect links to a non-category page.
category_redirect-problem-redirects: Log message indicating category redirect redirects to a non-existing page.
category_redirect-problem-self-linked: Log message indicating category redirect redirects to itself.
